{
  "texts": [
    "Finally, there are more sophisticated prompting strategies that may further improve model performance but were beyond the scope of this work.",
    "For example, exploring the utility of chain-of-thoughts 23 and automating prompt tuning strategies for biomedical NLP tasks is an area of promising future research.",
    "[24] [25] [26] These findings provide a comprehensive evaluation of the performance of LLMs on a variety of biomedical natural language processing tasks.",
    "The heterogeneity in results across prompting strategies, models, and datasets underscore the importance of evaluating the performance of a given model and prompt work for specific tasks.",
    "Our result has suggested great potential in adopting LLMs to execute biomedical tasks; yet it also showed the gap of only using the current stage LLMs for these tasks."
  ]
}